{"tid":2024681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂 抖陰而家喺香港appstore排緊第一喎","createTime":"2020-05-19T18:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T19:32:32.000Z","uid":315794,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d93ae1c54633eddb9e00e031e83caa592f37e925","tid":2024681,"uid":315794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T18:46:36.000Z","msg":"話說我啱啱見到隔離post<br />\n[國際] 印度佬開始瘋狂劣評抖音<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024375</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n啲印度佬洗到抖陰得返2星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就屎忽痕走去search吓抖陰喺香港做緊幾多星啦，點知一search，我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKZ2RwO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKZ2RwO.png&h=84eece8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻支那app喺香港app store做緊娛樂個rank第一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/360165o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F360165o.png&h=ad458876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁好唔 睇埋佢有幾多粒星啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JX0Dci.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JX0Dci.png&h=4eec63fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仆你個街，4.7，仲要有九成都係畀緊5星<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知香港係仲有好多港豬，但係屌你老母唔係咁呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋嚟重溫吓抖陰有咩仆街嘢先</span></span><br />\n1. 抖音ban鳩廣東話，逼人講支話。<br />\n呢樣前排好出名啦，係支那喺廣州做緊嘅種族滅絕政策之一。<br />\n2. Censorship<br />\n啦駛講啦屌。<br />\n3. 偷鳩你資料送畀北京。<br />\n哇屌你老母呢個犀鳩利，上面兩個都淨係支版抖音先會有，呢個係連國際版TikTok都會有，佢send畀北京server嘅唔單止係run拼音嘅必要數據，仲有好多用唔着嘅資料，<span style=\"color: red;\">呢度係講緊其他app嘅資料</span>。<br />\n<br />\n咁可以點做呢？<br />\n我拋個磚先。<br />\n首先，喺appstore download抖音，down完<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好開</span>，如果唔係你嘅資料就會<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TKH4kuc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKH4kuc.jpg&h=52d6f983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後，即刻碌落去，畀負皮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAhWV2N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAhWV2N.png&h=ab6b3d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似印度佬咁洗到佢得返兩粒星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗完記得del返個垃圾app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQAdYhT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQAdYhT.png&h=311e2e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係呢個方法有個好撚大嘅問題，就係唔夠人做嘅話就會推高佢個download，但係佢個分又唔會減好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n睇吓連登仔有咩好方法啦。"},{"pid":"02dd081bf147e2cb41f16f34b0aeb8df4292d4e3","tid":2024681,"uid":315794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T18:46:59.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d951a646e7ef0b589e38c0fa5005384793ab5146","tid":2024681,"uid":60749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T18:49:32.000Z","msg":"喺download嗰陣即刻去俾1星 之後再stop個download<br />\n佢就唔會計你download 但照計星"},{"pid":"4998a487dfc6b37ca6cf65bf0923b1901a7f32d3","tid":2024681,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T18:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac4cdedcf82ad2fe71d55c509b2ab65151a4b805","tid":2024681,"uid":315794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d951a646e7ef0b589e38c0fa5005384793ab5146","tid":2024681,"uid":60749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T18:49:32.000Z","msg":"喺download嗰陣即刻去俾1星 之後再stop個download<br />\n佢就唔會計你download 但照計星"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T18:50:27.000Z","msg":"醒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4745344e0d3174b10694ba2162a866bc666704","tid":2024681,"ui